<h1> Simple Spaghetti Bolognaise </h1>
<img src="spaghetti.jpg" title="Simple Spaghetti Bolognaise" alt= "Simple Spaghetti Bolognaise" width="450" height="300">
<h1> INGREDIENTS </h1>
<ul>
	<li> 500g beef minced </li>
	<li> 1 tbsp olive oil </li>
	<li> 1 onion, finely chopped </li>
	<li> 1 cup beef stock </li>
	<li> Clove of garlic </li>
	<li> Carrots, mushroom and celery (optional) </li>
	<li> 1 tsp dried mixed or italian-style herbs </li>
	<li> Squirt of tomato paste </li>
	<li> 1x425g passatta or chopped tomatoes </li>
</ul>

<h1> METHOD </h1>
<ol>
	<li> Heat oil in a heavy-based pan and add onion, stirring over a moderate heat 
		<br> for 1-2 minutes.</li>
	<li> Add mince, stirring constantly until well browned </li>
